						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Pillar in the temple of Kallēs11vara.</hi></p>						

						<p>A.D. 1293.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record is dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1215, Vijaya, [Mārga]śira śu 5, Thursday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1293, November 4.</hi> The week-day was <hi rend="bold">Wednesday.</hi> The following Thursday was a day of <hi rend="italic">s11ūnya-tithi.</hi></p>						

						<p>It registers a grant of land by <hi rend="bold">Viṭharasa,</hi> the officer-in-charge of taxes, and others for worship and offerings to a god (name lost).</p>						

						</summary>
